content: अजित {%<ab>a.</ab>%} {@--1@} Invincible, unconquerable, irresistible; °तं पुण्यं… महः <ls>U. 5. 27.</ls> {@--2@} Not conquered or won (as a country &c.); not restrained, curbed, controlled, °आत्मन्; °इंद्रिय of uncontrolled soul or passion. --तः {@--1@} <ab>N.</ab> of Viṣṇu or Śiva or of Buddha. {@--2@} <ab>N.</ab> of a powerful antidote, or a poisonous sort of rat. --(<ab>pl.</ab>) A class of deities in the first Manvantara.
